#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an5.180"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.180:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.180:0.2"
msgid "18. Upāsakavagga "
msgstr "18. A Lay Follower "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.180:0.3"
msgid "180. Gavesīsutta "
msgstr "180. About Gavesī "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an5.180:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosalesu cārikaṃ carati mahatā bhikkhusaṃghena saddhiṃ. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was wandering in the land of the Kosalans together with a large Saṅgha of mendicants. "

msgctxt "an5.180:1.2"
msgid "Addasā kho bhagavā addhānamaggappaṭipanno aññatarasmiṃ padese mahantaṃ sālavanaṃ; "
msgstr "While traveling along a road the Buddha saw a large sal grove in a certain spot. "

#. VAR: disvāna → disvā (bj, pts1)
#. VAR: okkamma → ukkamma (katthaci)
msgctxt "an5.180:1.3"
msgid "disvāna maggā okkamma yena taṃ sālavanaṃ tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā taṃ sālavanaṃ ajjhogāhetvā aññatarasmiṃ padese sitaṃ pātvākāsi. "
msgstr "He left the road, went to the sal grove, and plunged deep into it. And at a certain spot he smiled. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.215, sc2
msgctxt "an5.180:2.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmato ānandassa etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then Venerable Ānanda thought, "

msgctxt "an5.180:2.2"
msgid "“ko nu kho hetu ko paccayo bhagavato sitassa pātukammāya? "
msgstr "“What is the cause, what is the reason why the Buddha smiled? "

msgctxt "an5.180:2.3"
msgid "Na akāraṇena tathāgatā sitaṃ pātukarontī”ti. "
msgstr "Realized Ones do not smile for no reason.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.180:2.4"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā ānando bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "So Venerable Ānanda said to the Buddha, "

msgctxt "an5.180:2.5"
msgid "“ko nu kho, bhante, hetu ko paccayo bhagavato sitassa pātukammāya? "
msgstr "“What is the cause, what is the reason why the Buddha smiled? "

msgctxt "an5.180:2.6"
msgid "Na akāraṇena tathāgatā sitaṃ pātukarontī”ti. "
msgstr "Realized Ones do not smile for no reason.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an5.180:3.1"
msgid "“Bhūtapubbaṃ, ānanda, imasmiṃ padese nagaraṃ ahosi iddhañceva phītañca bahujanaṃ ākiṇṇamanussaṃ. "
msgstr "“Once upon a time, Ānanda, there was a city in this spot that was successful and prosperous and full of people. "

msgctxt "an5.180:3.2"
msgid "Taṃ kho panānanda, nagaraṃ kassapo bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho upanissāya vihāsi. "
msgstr "And Kassapa, a blessed one, a perfected one, a fully awakened Buddha, lived supported by that city. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.180:3.3"
msgid "Kassapassa kho panānanda, bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa gavesī nāma upāsako ahosi sīlesu aparipūrakārī. "
msgstr "He had a lay follower called Gavesī who had not fulfilled all the precepts. "

#. VAR: samādapitāni → samādāpitāni (?)
msgctxt "an5.180:3.4"
msgid "Gavesinā kho, ānanda, upāsakena pañcamattāni upāsakasatāni paṭidesitāni samādapitāni ahesuṃ sīlesu aparipūrakārino. "
msgstr "And the five hundred lay followers who were taught and advised by Gavesī also had not fulfilled all the precepts. "

msgctxt "an5.180:3.5"
msgid "Atha kho, ānanda, gavesissa upāsakassa etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then Gavesī thought: "

#. VAR: bahūpakāro → bahukāro (katthaci)
#. VAR: samādapetā → samādāpetā (?)
msgctxt "an5.180:3.6"
msgid "‘ahaṃ kho imesaṃ pañcannaṃ upāsakasatānaṃ bahūpakāro pubbaṅgamo samādapetā, ahañcamhi sīlesu aparipūrakārī, imāni ca pañca upāsakasatāni sīlesu aparipūrakārino. "
msgstr "‘I’m the helper, leader, and adviser of these five hundred lay followers, yet neither I nor they have fulfilled the precepts. "

msgctxt "an5.180:3.7"
msgid "Iccetaṃ samasamaṃ, natthi kiñci atirekaṃ; "
msgstr "We’re the same, I’m in no way better. "

msgctxt "an5.180:3.8"
msgid "handāhaṃ atirekāyā’ti. "
msgstr "So let me do better.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.216, sc4
msgctxt "an5.180:4.1"
msgid "Atha kho, ānanda, gavesī upāsako yena tāni pañca upāsakasatāni tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā tāni pañca upāsakasatāni etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Gavesī went to those five hundred lay followers and said to them: "

msgctxt "an5.180:4.2"
msgid "‘ajjatagge maṃ āyasmanto sīlesu paripūrakāriṃ dhārethā’ti. "
msgstr "‘From this day forth may the venerables remember me as one who has fulfilled the precepts.’ "

msgctxt "an5.180:4.3"
msgid "Atha kho, ānanda, tesaṃ pañcannaṃ upāsakasatānaṃ etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then those five hundred lay followers thought: "

msgctxt "an5.180:4.4"
msgid "‘ayyo kho gavesī amhākaṃ bahūpakāro pubbaṅgamo samādapetā. "
msgstr "‘The venerable Gavesī is our helper, leader, and adviser, "

msgctxt "an5.180:4.5"
msgid "Ayyo hi nāma gavesī sīlesu paripūrakārī bhavissati. "
msgstr "and now he will fulfill the precepts. "

#. VAR: Kimaṅgaṃ → kimaṅga (bj, pts1)
#. VAR: pana mayan’ti → pana na mayanti (bj)
msgctxt "an5.180:4.6"
msgid "Kimaṅgaṃ pana mayan’ti. "
msgstr "Why don’t we do the same?’ "

msgctxt "an5.180:4.7"
msgid "Atha kho, ānanda, tāni pañca upāsakasatāni yena gavesī upāsako tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā gavesiṃ upāsakaṃ etadavocuṃ: "
msgstr "Then those five hundred lay followers went to Gavesī and said to him: "

msgctxt "an5.180:4.8"
msgid "‘ajjatagge ayyo gavesī imānipi pañca upāsakasatāni sīlesu paripūrakārino dhāretū’ti. "
msgstr "‘From this day forth may Venerable Gavesī remember these five hundred lay followers as having fulfilled the precepts.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.180:4.9"
msgid "Atha kho, ānanda, gavesissa upāsakassa etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then Gavesī thought: "

msgctxt "an5.180:4.10"
msgid "‘ahaṃ kho imesaṃ pañcannaṃ upāsakasatānaṃ bahūpakāro pubbaṅgamo samādapetā, ahañcamhi sīlesu paripūrakārī, imānipi pañca upāsakasatāni sīlesu paripūrakārino. "
msgstr "‘I’m the helper, leader, and adviser of these five hundred lay followers, and both I and they have fulfilled the precepts. "

msgctxt "an5.180:4.11"
msgid "Iccetaṃ samasamaṃ, natthi kiñci atirekaṃ; "
msgstr "We’re the same, I’m in no way better. "

msgctxt "an5.180:4.12"
msgid "handāhaṃ atirekāyā’ti. "
msgstr "So let me do better.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an5.180:5.1"
msgid "Atha kho, ānanda, gavesī upāsako yena tāni pañca upāsakasatāni tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā tāni pañca upāsakasatāni etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Gavesī went to those five hundred lay followers and said to them: "

msgctxt "an5.180:5.2"
msgid "‘ajjatagge maṃ āyasmanto brahmacāriṃ dhāretha ārācāriṃ virataṃ methunā gāmadhammā’ti. "
msgstr "‘From this day forth may the venerables remember me as one who is celibate, set apart, avoiding the common practice of sex.’ "

msgctxt "an5.180:5.3"
msgid "Atha kho, ānanda, tesaṃ pañcannaṃ upāsakasatānaṃ etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then those five hundred lay followers did the same. … "

msgctxt "an5.180:5.4"
msgid "‘ayyo kho gavesī amhākaṃ bahūpakāro pubbaṅgamo samādapetā. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an5.180:5.5"
msgid "Ayyo hi nāma gavesī brahmacārī bhavissati ārācārī virato methunā gāmadhammā. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an5.180:5.6"
msgid "Kimaṅgaṃ pana mayan’ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an5.180:5.7"
msgid "Atha kho, ānanda, tāni pañca upāsakasatāni yena gavesī upāsako tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā gavesiṃ upāsakaṃ etadavocuṃ: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an5.180:5.8"
msgid "‘ajjatagge ayyo gavesī imānipi pañca upāsakasatāni brahmacārino dhāretu ārācārino viratā methunā gāmadhammā’ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.180:5.9"
msgid "Atha kho, ānanda, gavesissa upāsakassa etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then Gavesī thought: "

#. VAR: bahūpakāro → bahupakāro (bj)
msgctxt "an5.180:5.10"
msgid "‘ahaṃ kho imesaṃ pañcannaṃ upāsakasatānaṃ bahūpakāro pubbaṅgamo samādapetā. "
msgstr "‘These five hundred lay followers … "

msgctxt "an5.180:5.11"
msgid "Ahañcamhi sīlesu paripūrakārī. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an5.180:5.12"
msgid "Imānipi pañca upāsakasatāni sīlesu paripūrakārino. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an5.180:5.13"
msgid "Ahañcamhi brahmacārī ārācārī virato methunā gāmadhammā. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an5.180:5.14"
msgid "Imānipi pañca upāsakasatāni brahmacārino ārācārino viratā methunā gāmadhammā. "
msgstr "are celibate, set apart, avoiding the common practice of sex. "

msgctxt "an5.180:5.15"
msgid "Iccetaṃ samasamaṃ, natthi kiñci atirekaṃ; "
msgstr "We’re the same, I’m in no way better. "

msgctxt "an5.180:5.16"
msgid "handāhaṃ atirekāyā’ti. "
msgstr "So let me do better.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.217, sc6
msgctxt "an5.180:6.1"
msgid "Atha kho, ānanda, gavesī upāsako yena tāni pañca upāsakasatāni tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā tāni pañca upāsakasatāni etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Gavesī went to those five hundred lay followers and said to them: "

msgctxt "an5.180:6.2"
msgid "‘ajjatagge maṃ āyasmanto ekabhattikaṃ dhāretha rattūparataṃ virataṃ vikālabhojanā’ti. "
msgstr "‘From this day forth may the venerables remember me as one who eats in one part of the day, abstaining from eating at night, and from food at the wrong time.’ "

msgctxt "an5.180:6.3"
msgid "Atha kho, ānanda, tesaṃ pañcannaṃ upāsakasatānaṃ etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then those five hundred lay followers did the same. … "

msgctxt "an5.180:6.4"
msgid "‘ayyo kho gavesī bahūpakāro pubbaṅgamo samādapetā. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an5.180:6.5"
msgid "Ayyo hi nāma gavesī ekabhattiko bhavissati rattūparato virato vikālabhojanā. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an5.180:6.6"
msgid "Kimaṅgaṃ pana mayan’ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an5.180:6.7"
msgid "Atha kho, ānanda, tāni pañca upāsakasatāni yena gavesī upāsako tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā gavesiṃ upāsakaṃ etadavocuṃ: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an5.180:6.8"
msgid "‘ajjatagge ayyo gavesī imānipi pañca upāsakasatāni ekabhattike dhāretu rattūparate virate vikālabhojanā’ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.180:6.9"
msgid "Atha kho, ānanda, gavesissa upāsakassa etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then Gavesī thought: "

msgctxt "an5.180:6.10"
msgid "‘ahaṃ kho imesaṃ pañcannaṃ upāsakasatānaṃ bahūpakāro pubbaṅgamo samādapetā. "
msgstr "‘These five hundred lay followers … "

msgctxt "an5.180:6.11"
msgid "Ahañcamhi sīlesu paripūrakārī. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an5.180:6.12"
msgid "Imānipi pañca upāsakasatāni sīlesu paripūrakārino. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an5.180:6.13"
msgid "Ahañcamhi brahmacārī ārācārī virato methunā gāmadhammā. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an5.180:6.14"
msgid "Imānipi pañca upāsakasatāni brahmacārino ārācārino viratā methunā gāmadhammā. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an5.180:6.15"
msgid "Ahañcamhi ekabhattiko rattūparato virato vikālabhojanā. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an5.180:6.16"
msgid "Imānipi pañca upāsakasatāni ekabhattikā rattūparatā viratā vikālabhojanā. "
msgstr "eat in one part of the day, abstaining from eating at night, and food at the wrong time. "

msgctxt "an5.180:6.17"
msgid "Iccetaṃ samasamaṃ, natthi kiñci atirekaṃ; "
msgstr "We’re the same, I’m in no way better. "

msgctxt "an5.180:6.18"
msgid "handāhaṃ atirekāyā’ti. "
msgstr "So let me do better.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "an5.180:7.1"
msgid "Atha kho, ānanda, gavesī upāsako yena kassapo bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā kassapaṃ bhagavantaṃ arahantaṃ sammāsambuddhaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then the lay follower Gavesī went up to the blessed one Kassapa, the perfected one, the fully awakened Buddha and said to him: "

msgctxt "an5.180:7.2"
msgid "‘labheyyāhaṃ, bhante, bhagavato santike pabbajjaṃ labheyyaṃ upasampadan’ti. "
msgstr "‘Sir, may I receive the going forth, the ordination in the Buddha’s presence?’ "

msgctxt "an5.180:7.3"
msgid "Alattha kho, ānanda, gavesī upāsako kassapassa bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa santike pabbajjaṃ, alattha upasampadaṃ. "
msgstr "And he received the going forth, the ordination in the Buddha’s presence. "

msgctxt "an5.180:7.4"
msgid "Acirūpasampanno kho panānanda, gavesī bhikkhu eko vūpakaṭṭho appamatto ātāpī pahitatto viharanto nacirasseva—yassatthāya kulaputtā sammadeva agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajanti, tadanuttaraṃ—brahmacariyapariyosānaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja vihāsi. "
msgstr "Not long after his ordination, the mendicant Gavesī, living alone, withdrawn, diligent, keen, and resolute, realized the supreme culmination of the spiritual path in this very life. He lived having achieved with his own insight the goal for which gentlemen rightly go forth from the lay life to homelessness. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.180:7.5"
msgid "‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti abbhaññāsi. "
msgstr "He understood: ‘Rebirth is ended; the spiritual journey has been completed; what had to be done has been done; there is no return to any state of existence.’ "

msgctxt "an5.180:7.6"
msgid "Aññataro ca panānanda, gavesī bhikkhu arahataṃ ahosi. "
msgstr "And the mendicant Gavesī became one of the perfected. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.218, sc8
msgctxt "an5.180:8.1"
msgid "Atha kho, ānanda, tesaṃ pañcannaṃ upāsakasatānaṃ etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then those five hundred lay followers thought: "

msgctxt "an5.180:8.2"
msgid "‘ayyo kho gavesī amhākaṃ bahūpakāro pubbaṅgamo samādapetā. "
msgstr "‘Venerable Gavesī is our helper, leader, and adviser, "

msgctxt "an5.180:8.3"
msgid "Ayyo hi nāma gavesī kesamassuṃ ohāretvā kāsāyāni vatthāni acchādetvā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajissati. "
msgstr "He has shaved off his hair and beard, dressed in ocher robes, and gone forth from the lay life to homelessness. "

msgctxt "an5.180:8.4"
msgid "Kimaṅgaṃ pana mayan’ti. "
msgstr "Why don’t we do the same?’ "

msgctxt "an5.180:8.5"
msgid "Atha kho, ānanda, tāni pañca upāsakasatāni yena kassapo bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā kassapaṃ bhagavantaṃ arahantaṃ sammāsambuddhaṃ etadavocuṃ: "
msgstr "Then those five hundred lay followers went up to the blessed one Kassapa, the perfected one, the fully awakened Buddha and said to him: "

msgctxt "an5.180:8.6"
msgid "‘labheyyāma mayaṃ, bhante, bhagavato santike pabbajjaṃ, labheyyāma upasampadan’ti. "
msgstr "‘Sir, may we receive the going forth and ordination in the Buddha’s presence?’ "

msgctxt "an5.180:8.7"
msgid "Alabhiṃsu kho, ānanda, tāni pañca upāsakasatāni kassapassa bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa santike pabbajjaṃ, alabhiṃsu upasampadaṃ. "
msgstr "And they did receive the going forth and ordination in the Buddha’s presence. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "an5.180:9.1"
msgid "Atha kho, ānanda, gavesissa bhikkhuno etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then the mendicant Gavesī thought: "

msgctxt "an5.180:9.2"
msgid "‘ahaṃ kho imassa anuttarassa vimuttisukhassa nikāmalābhī homi akicchalābhī akasiralābhī. "
msgstr "‘I get the supreme bliss of freedom whenever I want, without trouble or difficulty. "

msgctxt "an5.180:9.3"
msgid "Aho vatimānipi pañca bhikkhusatāni imassa anuttarassa vimuttisukhassa nikāmalābhino assu akicchalābhino akasiralābhino’ti. "
msgstr "Oh, may these five hundred mendicants do the same!’ "

#. VAR: bhikkhusatāni vūpakaṭṭhā → bhikkhusatāni ekekā vūpakaṭṭhā (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "an5.180:9.4"
msgid "Atha kho, ānanda, tāni pañca bhikkhusatāni vūpakaṭṭhā appamattā ātāpino pahitattā viharantā nacirasseva—yassatthāya kulaputtā sammadeva agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajanti, tadanuttaraṃ—"
msgstr "Then those five hundred mendicants, living alone, withdrawn, diligent, keen, and resolute, soon realized the supreme culmination of the spiritual path in this very life. They lived having achieved with their own insight the goal for which gentlemen rightly go forth from the lay life to homelessness. "

msgctxt "an5.180:9.5"
msgid "brahmacariyapariyosānaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja vihariṃsu. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.180:9.6"
msgid "‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti abbhaññiṃsu. "
msgstr "They understood: ‘Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any state of existence.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc10
#. VAR: uttaruttari → uttaruttariṃ (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an5.180:10.1"
msgid "Iti kho, ānanda, tāni pañca bhikkhusatāni gavesīpamukhāni uttaruttari paṇītapaṇītaṃ vāyamamānā anuttaraṃ vimuttiṃ sacchākaṃsu. "
msgstr "And so, Ānanda, those five hundred mendicants headed by Gavesī, trying to go higher and higher, better and better, realized the supreme bliss of freedom. "

msgctxt "an5.180:10.2"
msgid "Tasmātiha, ānanda, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ: "
msgstr "So you should train like this: "

msgctxt "an5.180:10.3"
msgid "‘uttaruttari paṇītapaṇītaṃ vāyamamānā anuttaraṃ vimuttiṃ sacchikarissāmā’ti. "
msgstr "‘Trying to go higher and higher, better and better, we will realize the supreme bliss of freedom.’ "

msgctxt "an5.180:10.4"
msgid "Evañhi vo, ānanda, sikkhitabban”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how you should train.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.180:10.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.180:10.6"
msgid "Upāsakavaggo tatiyo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.219, sc11
msgctxt "an5.180:11.1"
msgid "Sārajjaṃ visārado nirayaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.180:11.2"
msgid "Veraṃ caṇḍālapañcamaṃ; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.180:11.3"
msgid "Pīti vaṇijjā rājāno, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.180:11.4"
msgid "Gihī ceva gavesināti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
